OL,3,CAt least 12 shot at an Ohio festival,
OL,4,Cwith search for suspects still ongoing
OL,6,FGunfire erupted on Saturday near a
OL,7,Fbusy street festival in Ohio, wounding
OL,8,Fat least 12 people and sending some
OL,9,Feventgoers scrambling for cover while
OL,10,Fothers rushed to help the victims.
OL,12,FNo suspects were in custody hours
OL,13,Fafterwards, Toledo Deputy Police Chief
OL,14,FJoe Heffernan said, and officials
OL,15,Furged people who were at the festival
OL,16,Fto come forward with any photos or
OL,17,Fvideos on their phones for possible
OL,18,Fleads.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
