OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780876973
OL,3,CAt least 12 shot at an Ohio festival,
OL,4,Cwith search for suspects still ongoing
OL,6,FThe shooting happened near the Old
OL,7,FWest End Festival, an annual gathering
OL,8,Fof live music and home tours.
OL,10,FHeffernan said it appeared that at
OL,11,Fleast two people fired weapons, and
OL,12,Fthey were "probably shooting at each
OL,13,Fother."
OL,15,FTwo of the victims were in critical
OL,16,Fcondition, Heffernan added. The ages
OL,17,Fof the victims ranged from 14 to 61,
OL,18,Fwith most of them in their early 20s.
OL,26,@tD@KOUuD@GO]
