OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780876973
OL,3,CAt least 12 shot at an Ohio festival,
OL,4,Cwith search for suspects still ongoing
OL,6,F"I am deeply concerned about the
OL,7,Fsituation in Toledo tonight," Ohio
OL,8,FGovernor Mike DeWine said in a
OL,9,Fstatement. "Summer festivals should be
OL,10,Fsafe spaces for families to spend time
OL,11,Ftogether without fear of violence."
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FMultiple videos posted to social media
OL,19,Fshowed people running amid the sound
OL,20,Fof gunshots and emergency officials
OL,21,Ftending to others who appeared wounded.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@]O]qD@LOUsD@cO]
