PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780876973
OL,3,CAt least 12 shot at an Ohio festival,
OL,4,Cwith search for suspects still ongoing
OL,6,FFire Chief Allison Armstrong said it
OL,7,Fwas difficult to get to the hospital
OL,8,Fdue to closed roads and traffic from
OL,9,Fpeople leaving the festival, but
OL,10,Femergency responders were able to
OL,11,Ftransport all patients from the scene
OL,12,Fwithin an hour.
OL,14,FKevin Berry was sitting in the
OL,15,Fneighbourhood arboretum listening to
OL,16,Flive music with friends when he heard
OL,17,Fa handful of gunshots ring out.
OL,19,F"Everybody hit the deck," he said.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
