PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780876973
OL,3,CAt least 12 shot at an Ohio festival,
OL,4,Cwith search for suspects still ongoing
OL,6,FWhen Berry looked back up, he saw a
OL,7,Fgun being tossed to the ground less
OL,8,Fthan 50 feet (15 meters) away from
OL,9,Fhim. Officers who were already on site
OL,10,Ffor the festival responded immediately.
OL,12,FBerry, who has medical training and
OL,13,Fserved in the Navy, walked around
OL,14,Flooking for anyone who might need help
OL,15,Fand saw at least five people with
OL,16,Fgunshot wounds.
OL,18,F"The folks who were hit were spread
OL,19,Fout around the arboretum area," he
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,26,@zD@AOU{D@_O]
