PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780876973
OL,3,CAt least 12 shot at an Ohio festival,
OL,4,Cwith search for suspects still ongoing
OL,6,FThe Old West End Festival is a two-day
OL,7,Fcelebration in Toledo's historic
OL,8,Fdistrict that includes live music,
OL,9,Ffood vendors, home tours and shopping.
OL,10,FBerry described it as the "kick-off to
OL,11,FToledo's summer festival season."
OL,13,FGeorge Kral, safety director for the
OL,14,Fcity, said officials were discussing
OL,15,Fwith organisers whether it would
OL,16,Fcontinue through the weekend.
OL,18,F"This is one of the most iconic
OL,19,Ffestivals in Toledo," he said, "and
OL,20,Fit's a shame that something like this
OL,21,Fhad to ruin it."
